<div class="policy-page full-width">
  <div class="policy-page-inner">
    <div class="policy-header text-center">
      <h1 class="policy-page-title">Find Your Perfect Fit</h1>
      <p class="policy-subtitle">Arlena Jewellery Sizing Guide</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="policy-page-content">
      <div class="intro-box">
        <p>Choosing the right ring size is important for a comfortable and secure fit. For the most accurate result, we recommend having your finger professionally measured by a jeweller.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Measure a Ring That Already Fits</h2>
        <p>If you have a ring that fits comfortably:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Choose a ring worn on the same finger and hand as your new ring.</li>
          <li>Measure the inside diameter of the ring from one inside edge to the other at its widest point.</li>
          <li>Compare your measurement with the size chart below.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Ring Size Chart</h2>
        <div style="overflow-x: auto;">
          <table class="size-chart-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>AU/UK Size</th>
                <th>US Size</th>
                <th>Inside Diameter</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>H</td><td>4</td><td>14.9 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>I</td><td>4.5</td><td>15.3 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>J</td><td>5</td><td>15.7 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>K</td><td>5.5</td><td>16.1 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>L</td><td>6</td><td>16.5 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>M</td><td>6.5</td><td>16.9 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>N</td><td>7</td><td>17.3 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>O</td><td>7.5</td><td>17.7 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>P</td><td>8</td><td>18.1 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Q</td><td>8.5</td><td>18.5 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>R</td><td>9</td><td>18.9 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>S</td><td>9.5</td><td>19.4 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>T</td><td>10</td><td>19.8 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>U</td><td>10.5</td><td>20.2 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>V</td><td>11</td><td>20.6 mm</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #666; font-style: italic; margin-top: 10px;">International size conversions are approximate and may vary slightly between sizing standards. Inside diameter should be used as the primary measurement reference.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <div class="pdf-download-box" style="margin: 30px 0;">
          <h4>Printable Ring Size Guide</h4>
          <p>Already have a ring that fits? Use our Printable Ring Size Guide to compare it against our actual-size ring circles and find your closest size.</p>
          <a href="{{ 'Arlena_Printable_Ring_Size_Guide.pdf' | file_url }}" class="pdf-download-btn" target="_blank" download>DOWNLOAD PRINTABLE RING SIZE GUIDE</a>
          <p class="pdf-download-note" style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 11px; color: #666;"><strong>Important:</strong> Print the guide at 100% / Actual Size. Do not select “Fit to Page” or “Scale to Fit”. Check the 50 mm calibration line before measuring to ensure the guide has printed at the correct scale.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Sizing Tips</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Measure the specific finger and hand where you intend to wear the ring.</li>
          <li>Measure when your hands are at a comfortable, normal temperature.</li>
          <li>Your fingers may change slightly in size throughout the day.</li>
          <li>A properly fitted ring should slide over your knuckle with slight resistance and sit comfortably once in place.</li>
          <li>Wider bands may feel more snug than narrower bands and may require a slightly different size.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .policy-page {
    background: #fff;
    min-height: 60vh;
    padding: 140px 20px 80px 20px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  .policy-page-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .policy-header {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    padding-bottom: 30px;
  }
  .policy-page-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #111;
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .policy-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-base);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #c5a880;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .policy-page-content {
    font-family: var(--font-base);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
  }
  .intro-box {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: #111;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .policy-section {
    margin-bottom: 45px;
  }
  .policy-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #111;
    margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f6f6f6;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .policy-section p {
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }
  .policy-section ol, .policy-section ul {
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .policy-section li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  
  /* Sizing Table */
  .size-chart-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 15px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .size-chart-table th {
    background: #111;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .size-chart-table td {
    padding: 8px 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    text-align: center;
    color: #333;
  }
  .size-chart-table tr:hover td {
    background-color: #fafafa;
  }

  .pdf-download-box {
    background-color: #faf7f2;
    border: 1px solid #eae1d4;
    padding: 25px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pdf-download-box h4 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #111;
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }
  .pdf-download-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #111;
    color: #fff !important;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    margin-top: 10px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .pdf-download-btn:hover {
    background-color: #c5a880;
  }

  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .policy-page {
      padding-top: 110px;
    }
    .policy-page-title {
      font-size: 26px;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Size Guide",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
